---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
---

<LandingLayout title="GEO - Generative Engine Optimization | Vanity Projects">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-purple-900 to-slate-900">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,')] opacity-40"></div>
		
		<div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 text-center">
			<div class="inline-block mb-6 px-4 py-2 bg-purple-500/20 border border-purple-400/30 rounded-full">
				<span class="text-purple-300 text-sm font-medium">Pierwsza agencja GEO w Polsce</span>
			</div>
			
			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
				Zbuduj przewagę nad konkurencją<br />
				w <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400">wyszukiwaniu AI</span>
			</h1>
			
			<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				Zanim oni w ogóle zrozumieją co się dzieje
			</p>
			
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				Optymalizacja pod ChatGPT, Claude i Google AI zamiast tradycyjnego Google
			</p>
			
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
				<a href="#contact" class="px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-pink-700 transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
					Zarezerwuj bezpłatną konsultację
				</a>
				<a href="#problem" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all border border-white/20">
					Dowiedz się więcej
				</a>
			</div>
			
			<div class="mt-16 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 text-gray-400 text-sm">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
					</svg>
					<span>800% wzrost wyszukiwań AI rok do roku</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
					</svg>
					<span>40% wzrost widoczności z GEO</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
					</svg>
					<span>Tylko 10 miejsc dostępnych</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Problem Section -->
	<section id="problem" class="py-24 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
					Nowa rzeczywistość – AI jako doradca zakupowy
				</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Rewolucja już się dzieje – AI przejmuje decyzje zakupowe
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
				<div>
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-100">
							<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
									<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="text-gray-700 italic">"Gdzie kupić samochód hybrydowy w Gdańsku?"</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-100">
							<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
									<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="text-gray-700 italic">"Znajdź najlepszy salon fryzjerski dla mężczyzn w Warszawie"</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-100">
							<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
									<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="text-gray-700 italic">"Który dealer BMW ma najlepsze opinie?"</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div>
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl text-white">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Różnica jest kluczowa:</h3>
						
						<div class="space-y-6">
							<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-red-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
									<span class="text-red-400 font-bold">G</span>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold mb-1">Google pokazuje</p>
									<p class="text-gray-400">10 linków do wyboru</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							
							<div class="h-px bg-gray-700"></div>
							
							<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
									<span class="text-purple-400 font-bold">AI</span>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold mb-1">AI podaje</p>
									<p class="text-gray-400">2-3 konkretne rekomendacje</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 rounded-lg">
							<p class="text-red-300 font-semibold">
								Jeśli Twojej firmy nie ma w tych odpowiedziach – nie istniejesz w momencie decyzji zakupowej.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="text-center p-6">
					<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">25%</div>
					<p class="text-gray-600">spadek tradycyjnego wyszukiwania do 2026 (Gartner)</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center p-6">
					<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">40%</div>
					<p class="text-gray-600">więcej widoczności z optymalizacją GEO (Princeton University)</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center p-6">
					<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">100%</div>
					<p class="text-gray-600">zmiana w podejmowaniu decyzji zakupowych</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Solution Section -->
	<section id="solution" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-purple-50">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
					Czym jest GEO?
				</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Generative Engine Optimization to pozycjonowanie ofert handlowych w erze wyszukiwania AI
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-600">S</span>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">SEO</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Tradycyjne podejście</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Optymalizacja pod algorytmy Google</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Ranking w wynikach wyszukiwania (SERP)</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Słowa kluczowe i backlinki</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Użytkownik wybiera z 10 linków</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-pink-600 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg text-white">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-3xl font-bold">G</span>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">GEO</h3>
							<p class="text-purple-100">Nowe podejście</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-white mb-4 font-medium">Optymalizacja pod modele językowe AI</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-200 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Rekomendacje w odpowiedziach AI</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-200 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Optymalizacja semantyczna i wektorowa</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-200 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
							</svg>
							<span>AI podaje 2-3 konkretne sugestie</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-purple-100">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">Nasza metodologia GEO łączy:</h3>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
							<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Wyszukiwania semantyczne</p>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Optymalizacja znaczenia, nie słów kluczowych</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
							<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Wektoryzacja języka</p>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sposób w jaki AI rozumie treść</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
							<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Wzorce generacji AI</p>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Jak AI tworzy odpowiedzi</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
							<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Multiplatformowość</p>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Advantage Section -->
	<section id="advantage" class="py-24 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
					Przewaga konkurencyjna
				</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Bycie pionierem w GEO daje unikalne korzyści
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-purple-100">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Efekt sieciowy uczenia AI</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Modele AI uczą się wzorców i wzmacniają udane rekomendacje</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Pierwszy w branży = referencyjna firma dla AI</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Konkurenci muszą przebić Twoją ugruntowaną pozycję</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-purple-100">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Mierzalny wpływ na biznes</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
